{"tid":802782,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"見到啲MK夫婦係街邊嘈交就覺得好好笑","createTime":"2018-09-01T16:57:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-02T01:59:26.000Z","uid":140411,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d413ba5565bd17e8f2107016c8d21b4ae3581a09","tid":802782,"uid":140411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T16:57:18.000Z","msg":"是咁的，夜晚7點幾落街食飯嘅時候就見到有對MK夫妻，男嘅金毛、黑色貼身背心、紋曬身同推住架BB車，女嘅擔住口煙、染到個頭鬼五馬六，睇落兩個都係二十頭。佢地一路行一路嘈，大約聽到佢地講冇錢<br />\n<br />\nMk老公：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   Mk老婆：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n金毛夫：屌你咪掛住食煙啦，冇錢開飯仲食煙？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n食煙妻：屌，同你生左件唔食煙對唔住自己<br />\n<br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n夫：屌，早知你係咁，當初就唔溝你溝XXX啦（人名聽得唔太清楚）<br />\n<br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （心諗有早知就唔中出啦）<br />\n<br />\n妻：個女你自己湊埋，我去搵仔<br />\n<br />\n夫：好呀，我同你一拍兩散，你唔洗旨意去搵仔，返屋企含撚啦你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n早知就唔好做mk啦，扑野扑得你咁爽，家下中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申，青頭，覺得個女好慘"},{"pid":"158ea89cfbbb8aea7452f14a22ba97f5f225c995","tid":802782,"uid":180913,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T16:59:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大把啦呢d case <br />\n有幾奇"},{"pid":"cc3a458276b51a45fbb7105d4c3dedd5301cf95e","tid":802782,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T17:03:07.000Z","msg":"又有抖音題材<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我而家去拍抖音片<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cba9